name: vlm_gist

info.name: VLM-GIST
info.description: This dataset contains images annotated with unique and semantically rich descriptions, as well as bounding boxes and segmentation masks for all visible object instances. Images '00013.jpg' to '00054.jpg' are taken from the AgiBot World dataset.
info.author: Bastian Pätzold, Jan Nogga, and Sven Behnke
